  "response": "When visiting Bogot\u00e1 with children, here are some great activities:\n\n1. Family-friendly attractions:\n- Sim\u00f3n Bol\u00edvar Park (large urban park with playgrounds)\n- Planetarium\n- Bogot\u00e1 Children's Museum\n- Mundo Aventura Theme Park\n- Botanical Garden\n\n2. Educational experiences:\n- Gold Museum (interesting exhibits for kids)\n- Maloka Interactive Museum\n- Parque Explora (science and technology museum)\n- National Museum\n\n3. Outdoor activities:\n- Monserrate Cable Car ride\n- Usaqu\u00e9n neighborhood walking tour\n- Ciclov\u00eda (car-free streets on Sundays)\n- Bike tours\n- Parque Nacional Natural\n\n4. Cultural experiences:\n- La Candelaria historic district\n- Street art tours\n- Mercado de Paloquemao (local market)\n- Folkloric dance shows\n\n5. Animal-related activities:\n- Santamar\u00eda Bullring (educational tours)\n- Venue Zoo\n- Ecological walks in nearby nature reserves\n\n6. Entertainment:\n- Soccer matches\n- Shopping centers with kids' zones\n- Movie theaters\n- Family-friendly restaurants\n\nPro tip: Consider the altitude and weather when planning activities with children.",
